Package game.interfaces

package game.interfaces
  • Interfaces
    Class
    Description
    Communicative
    This interface represents the capability of an entity to communicate.
    Consumables
    The Consumables interface provides the contract for any item that could be consumed in the game.
    Growable
    The Growable interface represents an object that can grow into something else.
    MonsterFactory
    The MonsterFactory interface allows the creation of different types of MonsterFactories with varying spawn probabilities and spawned monsters.
    ProducesFruit
    The ProducesFruit interface represents an entity that is capable of producing fruit.
    Purchasable
    Interface representing an item that can be purchased by an actor.
    Sellable
    Interface to be implemented by items that can be sold within the game.
